# tag v1.4-mainnet. ALL 6 contracts owned by the 2-of-3 Safe at
# 0x10d6Ff4eb8372aE20638db1f87a60f31fdF13E0F.
#
# COPY THESE INTO .env.production OR YOUR VERCEL ENV BEFORE THE
